print(f'The ratio of the original width of the image to its height: {k}')
new_width = 550
dim = (new_width, int(new_width / k))
print(f'Width, height: {dim}')
resized_RGB_img = cv2.resize(RGB_img2, dim, interpolation = cv2.INTER_AREA)
plt.imshow(resized_RGB_img)
plt.show()
